name: Series 1: Fauna – 001 – Blue Morpho
description:
Blue Morpho butterfly from Fairchild Tropical Botanic Garden taken by KDW prior to being diagnosed with Parkinson’s Disease and Lewy Body Dementia. This photograph was taken January 18, 2013.

PreDiagnosedArt has been created to highlight art that was created prior to being diagnosed to make a positive impact from a dark situation. KDW is a photographer who has been to many places and enjoyed capturing those images he saw with photography. Majority of proceeds from pieces sold, that were created by KDW, will go to Parkinson’s related charities and assisting with his care.
